{"tid":266960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蛋撻食開酥皮定牛油皮？容海恩：唔係一樣㗎咩？","createTime":"2017-06-02T01:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T21:07:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":258,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03bfe7d8152cab8e5e5932294fb450620556cb45","tid":266960,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"新民黨立法會議員容海恩當年在選舉論壇上，以「不如你話我知」成為其金句，原來不單是政治問題上需要「攞貼士」，連蛋撻皮都不懂分辨。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170601/56770616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170601%2F56770616&d=88oHizLfb6OmYZ3Fk6n5jr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=15aa1e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170601%2F56770616&h=d593977e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170601/56770616</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170601/large/1496315500_06e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170601%2Flarge%2F1496315500_06e0.jpg&h=ca1d4a16&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n港青少年領袖發展協會主辦的「香港模擬立法會」近日上載宣傳片，其中一段邀請了容海恩「快問快答」，問到她食蛋撻喜歡牛油皮還是酥皮時，容竟一臉無知問「牛油皮同酥皮係咪即係一樣？」，主持被其答案嚇呆，一時未能反應，其後尷尬指「口感唔同」，容海恩大笑後反問「係用牛油搭出嚟？」<br />\n<br />\n主持繼續努力澄清牛油皮即是「曲奇皮」，容海恩再次「天真地」反問「曲奇皮？」，繼而稱自己未食過曲奇皮蛋撻，最後選擇酥皮蛋撻。<br />\n<br />\n容海恩不懂分辨蛋撻皮惹來網民嘲諷，有人留言揶揄叫主持不要問「咁難嘅問題」，笑指「牛油皮同酥皮佢點識分ar　#曲」。"},{"pid":"cea66836e4b283264063fe2589ff653147957b8b","tid":266960,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"牛油皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n酥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc7a0ecb6ec4f137b9cff7453aabb4ab8e3510f","tid":266960,"uid":2613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"